{
  "id": "69f5f3d0741e929390f2b967",
  "title": "井戸端チャット",
  "created": 1777726420,
  "updated": 1778318912,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f5f3d0741e929390f2b967",
      "text": "井戸端チャット",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726420,
      "updated": 1777726431
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f3e200000000004fde78",
      "text": "[チャット]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726434,
      "updated": 1777726651
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f3e200000000004fde79",
      "text": "　最初は記録を目的とせずリアルタイムの入力をお互いに楽しむ記事を作るのはどうだろうか？[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726434,
      "updated": 1777726710
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f45d00000000004fde7d",
      "text": "　\tインスタグラムのストーリーが近いかもしれない。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726557,
      "updated": 1777726568
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f46800000000004fde7f",
      "text": "　\tジャストアイデアから記事として議論を増やす場所になっても面白いと思う。",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726568,
      "updated": 1777726581
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f3e200000000004fde7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726434,
      "updated": 1777726434
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f3f400000000008e0743",
      "text": "時間経過で消えるとかがある想定?[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726453,
      "updated": 1777726468
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f3f600000000008e0744",
      "text": "\tそれができたら理想ではありますね、もしくは記事化して切り出しても良い。[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726455,
      "updated": 1777726494
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f40e00000000004fde7b",
      "text": " 日付+`chat`みたいな記事名にして1か月以上古いのは自動で消すとかかな〜[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726478,
      "updated": 1777726506
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f41900000000008e0745",
      "text": "\t\tもっと寿命が短くてもいいと思います、もはや記録に残らないレベルのものでも[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726489,
      "updated": 1777726524
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f43200000000004fde7c",
      "text": "　　アンケート",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726515,
      "updated": 1777726532
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f44300000000008e0747",
      "text": "　　\t1日：[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726532,
      "updated": 1777726548
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f45000000000008e074c",
      "text": "　　\t3日：[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726545,
      "updated": 1777726552
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f44600000000008e0748",
      "text": "　　\t1週間：[HelloPeople.icon][bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726534,
      "updated": 1777726569
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f44900000000008e074a",
      "text": "　　\t2週間:[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726537,
      "updated": 1777726570
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f44700000000008e0749",
      "text": "　　\t1か月:",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726536,
      "updated": 1777726554
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f4bf00000000008e074d",
      "text": "　　\t90日:",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726655,
      "updated": 1777726656
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f43800000000008e0746",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1777726525,
      "updated": 1777726525
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f4fd00000000004fde80",
      "text": "　消える仕組みも、記事自体が全面削除じゃなくて、追加された行の日付がしきい値の日数を超えたら削除されるのが良いと思う。[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726718,
      "updated": 1777726898
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f59a00000000004fde82",
      "text": "　\t他人の筆跡が次第に消えていく。といった感じ。[HelloPeople.icon]",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726874,
      "updated": 1777726900
    },
    {
      "id": "69f5f50500000000004fde81",
      "text": "\t\tこれ多分JS入れないと厳しそう",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
      "created": 1777726725,
      "updated": 1778318911
    },
    {
      "id": "69fefe3f00000000003c4410",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f938a902ea5180024085116",
